NK020(wa)002:0: rtsa dkyil sgrub dbang gi las byang khol bton bklag chog tu bkod pa bzhugs so //
NK020(wa)002:2: gang thugs mi 'gyur bde ba che'i //
NK020(wa)002:3: snang brnyan 'gag med zhi khro'i lhar //
NK020(wa)002:4: ston mdzad dpal ldan rdo rje sems //
NK020(wa)002:5: drin can bla ma'i zhabs la 'dud //
NK020(wa)002:6: bla med bskyed dang rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor khyad //
NK020(wa)002:7: bshad nas rgyud lugs gtsor byas chu bo bzhi //
NK020(wa)002:8: gang du bskur ba thun mong rtsa dkyil gyi //
NK020(wa)002:9: cho ga rje yi gsung la kha 'phang ston //
NK020(wa)002:10: de ltar yo ga man chad yan lag gi dkyil 'khor drug song nas /
NK020(wa)002:11: 'dir bla med kyi dkyil 'khor bshad pa la don gsum ste /
NK020(wa)002:12: nang dbang dang sgrub dbang gang du bskur bya'i /
NK020(wa)002:13: dkyil 'khor bdun pa dang brgyad pa'i khyad par bshad /
NK020(wa)002:14: des de dang de la dkyil 'khor so so ba med dam snyam pa'i log rtog bsal /
NK020(wa)002:15: da lta'i phyag bzhes ltar gyi sgrub dkyil rje bla mas mdzad pa la kha 'phang pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:17: nang dbang gang du bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK020(wa)002:18: sgrub dbang gang du bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK020(wa)002:19: dang po gzhan du shes par byas la /
NK020(wa)002:20: gnyis pa sgrub dbang gang du bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK020(wa)002:21: rtsa rgyud las gsungs pa dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor te /
NK020(wa)002:22: de yang ji ltar bskyed pa'i cho ga a nu'i theg pa rang lugs bzhin du /
NK020(wa)002:23: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad rang gi phung khams skye mched du 'du zhing /
NK020(wa)002:24: de nyid gdod nas lha'i rang bzhin du shes pas /
NK020(wa)002:25: lha rnams kyi gsang sngags brjod pa tsam gyi dwangs
NK020(wa)002:26: pa'i mtsho la gza' skar shar ba ltar cig car
NK020(wa)002:27: du gsal 'debs pa yin pas na /
NK020(wa)002:28: bskyed tshul dang cho ga ma gzhi rje'i sgrub thabs dngos grub char 'bebs ltar las /
NK020(wa)002:29: mi 'dra ba'i khyad par las kyi rim pa'i ting
NK020(wa)002:30: nge 'dzin dang rjes chog gi skabs su phra mo
NK020(wa)002:32: bye brag bskyed bya khro bo'i rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi ngo bo ches mi mthun pas /
NK020(wa)002:33: de dag gi kha bsgyur tshul ni /
NK020(wa)002:34: sngon 'gro las bdun dkyus bzhin song nas /
NK020(wa)002:35: dngos gzhi'i ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum las /
NK020(wa)002:37: mi gnas mi rtog bsam dang bral //
NK020(wa)002:38: ma chags chags bral yul las 'das //
NK020(wa)002:39: ci yang mi 'byung ci ma yin //
NK020(wa)002:40: rang byung rang zhi brjod dang bral //
NK020(wa)002:41: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad skye ba med
NK020(wa)002:42: pa'i dbyings ye ji bzhin pa kun tu bzang mo'i
NK020(wa)002:43: mkha' klong rnam par dag pa'i dkyil 'khor du gnas
NK020(wa)002:45: gnam sa ri brag dngos po cir snang yang /
NK020(wa)002:46: de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK020(wa)002:47: chos nyid stong pa nyid du don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)002:48: spros pa med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:52: yongs la khyab pa nyi ma'i 'od //
NK020(wa)002:53: snying rje byang chub sems yin te //
NK020(wa)002:54: rnam rtog mun pa sel bar snang //
NK020(wa)002:57: de bzhin nyid ma rtogs pa'i sgyu ma lta bu'i
NK020(wa)002:58: sems can rnams la 'gag med snying rje rig pa'i
NK020(wa)002:59: rtsal snang ye shes kun tu bzang po'i rol pa
NK020(wa)002:60: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor du snang bar
NK020(wa)002:62: ma rtog sems can sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:63: kun tu snang ba'i ting 'dzin bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK020(wa)002:64: chos nyid skye ba med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)002:65: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:69: a ni chags med yi ge'i mdzod //
NK020(wa)002:70: cho 'phrul rtog pa kun gyi rgyu //
NK020(wa)002:71: nyon mongs skyon bral zla ba'i mdog /
NK020(wa)002:74: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i sras bde
NK020(wa)002:75: ba chen po rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil
NK020(wa)002:76: 'khor a dkar po'i rang bzhin du snang bar bsam
NK020(wa)002:78: ma rigs sems kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:79: rgyu yi ting 'dzin bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:80: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)002:81: rang byung ye shes lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:85: rten gzhal yas khang bsgom pa dang /
NK020(wa)002:86: brten pa lha bsgom pa gnyis kyi /
NK020(wa)002:88: gzhi dbang chen gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa ni /
NK020(wa)002:89: rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi rgyu las /
NK020(wa)002:90: e yam ra sum kem ram /
NK020(wa)002:91: zhes cho 'phrul gyi rang sgrar grags pa las yum
NK020(wa)002:92: lnga'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa 'byung ba lnga'i
NK020(wa)002:93: dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis grub pa ni /
NK020(wa)002:94: rdo rje rin po che'i 'od snang bas kun tu mdangs phyungs pa'i mkha' la /
NK020(wa)002:95: rlung nag gi phung po rgya yongs su ma chad par mnyam pa /
NK020(wa)002:96: khrag gi phung po rba klong du 'khrugs pa rgya yongs su ma chad pa /
NK020(wa)002:99: rus pa'i phung po rgya kun tu mnyam pa'i gzhi la /
NK020(wa)002:101: asma gar+g+ha 'od 'khrigs pa'i nor bu rin po che 'bar ba'i brag gtams pa /
NK020(wa)002:102: bskal pa'i me'u phung po rab tu 'bar zhing 'khrugs pas 'byams klas par bsam mo //
NK020(wa)002:103: gnyis pa rten gzhal yas khang dngos bsgom pa ni /
NK020(wa)002:104: yum lnga'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa'i snying po las cho 'phrul gyi sgrar snang ba ni /
NK020(wa)002:105: b+ha ga gsang ba'i 'od zer las //
NK020(wa)002:106: bde gshegs bzhugs pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK020(wa)002:107: nam mkha'i mtha' ltar dpag tu med //
NK020(wa)002:108: dus gsum rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i dbyings //
NK020(wa)002:109: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he ka p+aa la b+h+r+aum /
NK020(wa)002:110: zhes pa'i sgra gdangs kyi rkyen las nam mkha' thams
NK020(wa)002:111: cad pho brang gi gzhal yas khang 'byams klas par
NK020(wa)002:112: grub pa ni / 'og khang 'bar ba'i gzhal yas phyi nang du rim pa lnga pa /
NK020(wa)002:114: ga bu chung brtsegs pa'i rtsigs pa la gnam lcags kyi gzer ta le bar btab pa /
NK020(wa)002:115: rtsibs kun tu nyi ma dang zla ba rangs pa dang ma rangs pa 'phyo ba /
NK020(wa)002:116: nya chen po'i ka gdung la /
NK020(wa)002:117: nya phran gyi dral grab gtams pa /
NK020(wa)002:120: sprul chun gyi ka rgyan la sogs pa /
NK020(wa)002:123: chos nyid kyi bla res rnam par brgyan pa /
NK020(wa)002:124: ye shes kyi lda ldis mngon par bres pa /
NK020(wa)002:125: rdo rje'i rgyan dang 'phan gyis klubs pa /
NK020(wa)002:126: sprin nag gi zar tshags dang /
NK020(wa)002:127: sprin nag gi grib so lta bus gzhol ba'i bar bar thams cad na /
NK020(wa)002:131: 'khor ba'i man+dala yo bkram pa la /
NK020(wa)002:136: rdo rjes kun tu spras pa /
NK020(wa)002:137: de nas khyams gru bzhi pa lnga rim phyogs mdog
NK020(wa)002:138: can gyi bar khyams bzhi la sgo sgo khyud can
NK020(wa)002:139: rgyan med pa gnyis gnyis te brgyad dang /
NK020(wa)002:140: phyi khyams lnga pa la sgo rta babs la sogs
NK020(wa)002:141: pa sgo rgyan dang ldan pa'i sgo dgus kun tu
NK020(wa)002:142: gsal bar gyur pa'i nang ma gru chad dang bcas
NK020(wa)002:143: pa'i lte ba re'u mig dgu pa /
NK020(wa)002:144: de'i phyir 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa drug rim gyis bskor pa'i lte ba dang /
NK020(wa)002:145: 'khor lo rim pa gnyis pa dang /
NK020(wa)002:146: drug pa gsum gyi mthar rdo rje dang /
NK020(wa)002:148: 'bar ba'i phreng ba ste mu khyud sum rim dang /
NK020(wa)002:149: 'khor lo rim pa gzhan bzhi la mu khyud rkyang pa re res bskor ba /
NK020(wa)002:150: phyi nas rim pa bzhin khyad par du gyur pas spags pa /
NK020(wa)002:151: pho brang dbus ma'i steng khang zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor chen por gnas pa ni /
NK020(wa)002:152: gru bzhi lham pa mdzes par snang //
NK020(wa)002:153: rin chen sna bzhi'i rgyu las grub //
NK020(wa)002:154: glo 'bur bzhi yang mkhar thabs tshul //
NK020(wa)002:155: rin chen bzhi las grub pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:156: bum pa'i rtse mo chos kyi tog /
NK020(wa)002:157: rma bya'i mdongs ltar ldan pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:158: sgo bzhi sgo khyud rnams kyis brgyan //
NK020(wa)002:159: rta babs brgyad dang yang dag ldan //
NK020(wa)002:160: dbus na 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa //
NK020(wa)002:161: lte bar bcas shing rtsibs brten ldan //
NK020(wa)002:162: gru chad bar khyams mdzes par 'bar //
NK020(wa)002:164: pho brang 'og ma'i sgo'i phyi khyams kyi khor yug zlum po pad+ma'i lte ba la rdzogs pa'i mthar /
NK020(wa)002:165: ru dra longs spyod dang bcas pa dbyings su bsgral ba'i dur khrod chen po brgyad /
NK020(wa)002:166: dur khrod kyi chos rnams kyis 'jigs par byas pa'i
NK020(wa)002:167: phyi nang rdo rje srung ba'i gur khang 'bar ba
NK020(wa)002:168: me'i 'od zer kun tu 'phro bas yongs su bskor
NK020(wa)002:169: ba'o // gsum pa gdan bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)002:170: dkyil 'khor 'og ma'i dbus kyi lte bar rdo rje
NK020(wa)002:171: brag chen gtams pa la pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma
NK020(wa)002:173: de'i steng du thabs shes nyi zla brtsegs pa la
NK020(wa)002:174: dbang phyug khyo shugs nyi shu rtsa bzhi rdzogs pa'i
NK020(wa)002:183: byol song gtso bo brgyad re res dregs pa pho mo mnan pa /
NK020(wa)002:184: de nas 'khor lo rnams kyi phyogs kyi rtsibs la pad+ma nyi zla dregs pa'i gdan dang /
NK020(wa)002:185: lha gnas rnams su nyi ma dang zhing gi gdan
NK020(wa)002:186: la sogs pa rigs dang mthun pa'i gdan re re
NK020(wa)002:187: / pho brang steng ma'i 'khor lo'i lte bar seng ge'i khri cha gnyis /
NK020(wa)002:191: shang shang gis btegs pa'i khri re re /
NK020(wa)002:192: de rnams kyi steng du pad nyi zla ba ste lnga brtsegs /
NK020(wa)002:193: sems dpa' brgyad kyi gnas su pad nyi zla ba /
NK020(wa)002:194: bya byed gnyis la rin po che'i khri dang pad nyi zla ba /
NK020(wa)002:195: thub pa drug la pad rkyang dang sgo ba bzhi
NK020(wa)002:196: la nyi ma'i gdan re re gsal bar bsgom la
NK020(wa)002:198: snod kyi 'jig rten 'byung ba cir snang yang /
NK020(wa)002:199: gzhal yas dbang chen bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:200: chos nyid mtha' dbus med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)002:201: 'og min gnas su lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:202: na mo h+aum dur khrod rdzas kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:203: 'bar ba'i gzhal yas bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:204: rdzas su lta ba rtog pa kun bral nas //
NK020(wa)002:205: gnas mchog rab 'byams lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:207: zhes pas gsal btab cing gzi byin bskyed do //
NK020(wa)002:208: gnyis pa brten pa lha bskyed pa la /
NK020(wa)002:209: ji ltar bsgom pa'i tshul dang /
NK020(wa)002:212: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad bdag gi phung khams skye mched du 'du la /
NK020(wa)002:213: de thams cad lha'i rang bzhin du ye nas sangs
NK020(wa)002:214: rgyas par shes pas lha rnams kyi gsang sngags chos
NK020(wa)002:215: nyid kyi rang sgrar bsgrags pa tsam gyis dwangs pa'i
NK020(wa)002:216: mtsho la nyi zla gza' skar cig car du shar
NK020(wa)002:220: dbang bskur byin rlabs bya ba gnyis kyi /
NK020(wa)002:222: steng khang zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK020(wa)002:223: 'og khang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK020(wa)002:224: phyi khyabs rig 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang gsum las dang po ni /
NK020(wa)002:227: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK020(wa)002:228: dbus kyi gdan la bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu
NK020(wa)002:229: bzang po mthing ga mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum
NK020(wa)002:230: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyi rdo rje dril
NK020(wa)002:231: bu / gnyis pa byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya /
NK020(wa)002:232: gsum pa mnyam gzhag mdzad pa /
NK020(wa)002:233: kun tu bzang mo sngon mo dang 'khril ba /
NK020(wa)002:236: gtso bo'i mdun du mi bskyod pa sngon po mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi /
NK020(wa)002:237: dang po gnyis kyi rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK020(wa)002:239: gsum pas rin po che dang ral gri 'dzin pa
NK020(wa)002:240: dbyings phyug ma sngon mo rdor dril 'dzin pas 'khyud
NK020(wa)002:243: shar gyi rtsibs la rnam snang dkar po dkar sngo dkar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi /
NK020(wa)002:244: g.yas gsum 'khor lo rdo rje rin chen /
NK020(wa)002:245: g.yon gsum dril bu pad+ma ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)002:246: spyan ma dkar mo 'khor lo dang dril bu 'dzin pas 'khyud pa /
NK020(wa)002:249: lho'i rtsibs la rin chen 'byung ldan ser po ser sngo dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi /
NK020(wa)002:250: g.yas gsum rin chen rdo rje 'khor lo //
NK020(wa)002:251: g.yon gsum dril bu pad+ma ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)002:252: m+aa ma k+ai ser mo rin po che dang dril bu 'dzin pas 'khyud pa /
NK020(wa)002:255: nub kyi rtsibs la snang mtha' dmar po dmar dkar sngo ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi /
NK020(wa)002:256: g.yas gsum pad+ma rdo rje 'khor lo /
NK020(wa)002:257: g.yon gsum dril bu rin chen ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)002:258: gos dkar mo dmar mo pad+ma dang dril bu 'dzin pas 'khyud pa /
NK020(wa)002:259: h+aam pra dz+ny+aa d+h+rika t+aam badz+ra ra ti /
NK020(wa)002:260: byang gi rtsibs la don yod grub pa ljang gu ljang dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi /
NK020(wa)002:261: g.yas gsum ral gri rdo rje 'khor lo /
NK020(wa)002:262: g.yon gsum dril bu rin chen pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)002:263: dam tshig sgrol ma ljang gu ral gri dang dril bu 'dzin pas 'khyud pa /
NK020(wa)002:264: yab rnams rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung dang /
NK020(wa)002:265: yum rnams brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung gis rol ba'o //
NK020(wa)002:267: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba cir snang yang /
NK020(wa)002:268: rigs lnga yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:269: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)002:270: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK020(wa)002:272: 'khor lo'i mchan bzhi la shar lho nas rim pa bzhin /
NK020(wa)002:274: h+aum l+aa s+ye sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK020(wa)002:275: sa snying dkar po rin po che'i myu gu 'dzin pa sgeg mo dkar mo me long bsnams pa /
NK020(wa)002:277: tram m+aa l+ye sa ma ya hoh nam snying ser po ral gri /
NK020(wa)002:278: phreng ba ma ser mo rin po che'i phreng ba /
NK020(wa)002:279: h+r+aih h+aa h+aum pad+ma pra da ma /
NK020(wa)002:280: h+r+aim g+ai ti r+aa go ham /
NK020(wa)002:281: spyan ras gzigs dmar po pad+ma /
NK020(wa)002:282: glu ma dmar mo pi wam /
NK020(wa)002:284: am nirti r+aa ga ya mye /
NK020(wa)002:285: phyag rdor mthing ga rdo rje /
NK020(wa)002:286: gar ma ljang gu gar rgya mdzad pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:287: gru chad bzhi'i shar lho nas rim pa bzhin /
NK020(wa)002:288: mee d+h+aa ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:289: dzah d+h+au pe pra be sha /
NK020(wa)002:290: byams pa dkar ser klu shing /
NK020(wa)002:291: spos ma dkar ser spos khang /
NK020(wa)002:292: th+l+him nis+sa ram b+ha ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:295: me tog ma dmar ser me tog gi phreng ba /
NK020(wa)002:296: h+aum sa r+aa dz+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:297: bam d+ai pa su gi r+ai /
NK020(wa)002:298: kun bzang dmar ljang rin po che'i snye ma /
NK020(wa)002:299: mar me ma dmar ljang mar me /
NK020(wa)002:300: mum sh+r+ai am r+aa g+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:303: dri chab ma dkar ljang dung phor bsnams pa ste /
NK020(wa)002:304: yab rnams g.yon dril bu 'dzin cing phyed skyil gyis
NK020(wa)002:305: rol ba'i g.yon nas yum rnams g.yas dril bu 'dzin
NK020(wa)002:306: pas 'khyud pa / gshegs pa gshegs ma /
NK020(wa)002:307: sems dpa' sems ma de rnams dar dang rin po
NK020(wa)002:308: che'i rgyan sogs 'khor los sgyur ba'i cha lugs can
NK020(wa)002:310: dbang po rnam shes yul dus cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:311: sems dpa' sems ma bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:312: thams cad lha dang lha mo'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)002:313: rgyal ba'i sras su lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:316: khyams kyi shar du byed pa po kun tu bzang po mnyam bzhag skyil krung can /
NK020(wa)002:317: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK020(wa)002:318: khyams kyi nub tu kun tu bzang mo dkar mo chos 'byung gi phyag rgya can rgyan spangs pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:320: yid dang chos kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:321: kun bzang yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:322: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)002:323: chos sku 'gyur med lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:326: mu ne h+aum t+r+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:331: khyams kyi shar lhor lha'i thub pa dkar po pi wam /
NK020(wa)002:332: byang du lha min gyi thub pa mthing ga go cha /
NK020(wa)002:333: lhor mi'i thub pa ser po gseg par /
NK020(wa)002:334: nub byang du byol song gi thub pa dmar nag pusti /
NK020(wa)002:335: lho nub tu yi dwags kyi thub pa ser nag sgrom bu /
NK020(wa)002:336: byang shar du dmyal ba'i thub pa dud kha me chu 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)002:337: thams cad kyang mchog gi sprul sku'i cha byad can /
NK020(wa)002:338: 'gro ba'i don la bzhengs stabs kyis gnas pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:340: 'gro ba rigs drug dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:341: thub pa drug tu bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:342: rol pa cir yang snang ba'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)002:343: sangs rgyas mdzad pa lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:345: h+aum ya m+aan+ta kri ta phata /
NK020(wa)002:346: badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK020(wa)002:347: shar sgor gshin rje gshed smug nag n+ri mgo gdengs pa /
NK020(wa)002:348: lcags kyu ma smug nag lcags kyu 'dzin pa dang rol ba /
NK020(wa)002:350: rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+he lho sgor stobs po che ser nag rdo rje /
NK020(wa)002:351: zhags pa ma ser nag zhags pa 'dzin pa dang rol ba /
NK020(wa)002:353: pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+he nub sgor rta mgrin dmar nag thod dbyug sbrul gyis dkris pa /
NK020(wa)002:354: lcags sgrog ma dmar nag lcags sgrog 'dzin pa dang rol ba /
NK020(wa)002:356: karma d+ha ra ma h+aa byang sgor bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang nag rgya gram 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)002:357: dril bu ma ljang nag dril bu 'dzin pa dang rol ba /
NK020(wa)002:358: thams cad kyang khro gtum mi bzad pa'i nyams can gyad kyi dor stabs kyis bzhugs pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:360: yan lag bzhi yi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:361: sgo ba yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:362: yab yum 'du 'bral med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)002:363: phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:365: gnyis pa 'og khang khro ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa la gnyis las /
NK020(wa)002:366: dang po gtso bo bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)002:367: sa nga sh+r+ai he ru ka sarba ta th+aa ga
NK020(wa)002:368: ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra tsan+da sarba
NK020(wa)002:369: du sh+tan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK020(wa)002:370: h+aum s+w+aa h+aa / sa nga shwa ri kha mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:372: rgyu byang chub kyi sems nyid sngags kyi sgra gdangs kyis sad pa las /
NK020(wa)002:373: dbus kyi gdan la bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po
NK020(wa)002:374: rdo rje sa nga sh+r+ai he ru ka sku mdog
NK020(wa)002:375: mthing nag nyi ma bye ba'i 'od ltar 'bar ba'i
NK020(wa)002:376: gzi brjid can / zhal nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK020(wa)002:377: phyag bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis pa /
NK020(wa)002:378: rtsa zhal sku lus dang mtshungs pa /
NK020(wa)002:379: g.yas zhal gsum ser dmar ljang ba /
NK020(wa)002:380: g.yon zhal gsum dmar sngo ljang ba /
NK020(wa)002:381: de'i steng gi dbus zhal ser po //
NK020(wa)002:384: de'i steng gi dbus zhal mthing ga /
NK020(wa)002:389: kun gyi steng zhal dmar po rta skad 'tsher ba /
NK020(wa)002:390: zhal re re bzhin dmar la zlum pa'i spyan gsum gsum dang ldan cing /
NK020(wa)002:391: mche ba rnon po bzhi bzhi gtsigs pa /
NK020(wa)002:392: rnam par 'gyur ba'i khro gnyer can /
NK020(wa)002:394: dang po gnyis kyis kun bzang yab yum thugs kar
NK020(wa)002:395: bsnol nas 'dzin pa lhag ma g.yas kyi nyi shu
NK020(wa)002:396: na rigs lnga / sems dpa' brgyad /
NK020(wa)002:400: lha min gyi thub pa gsum /
NK020(wa)002:401: g.yon pa nyi shu na yum lnga /
NK020(wa)002:406: dmyal ba'i thub pa rnams 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)002:408: glang po che'i ko barlona pas ston g.yogs shing /
NK020(wa)002:409: stag gi lpags pa'i sham thabs grol ba /
NK020(wa)002:412: khrag zhag thal ba sogs dur khrod rol pa'i chas brgyad dang /
NK020(wa)002:413: dpal gyi chas brgyad rdzogs pa /
NK020(wa)002:417: rin po cher snang ba las rgyal byed dpal rtags kyi mtshan ma 'bar ba /
NK020(wa)002:418: gar gyi nyams dgus sgeg cing /
NK020(wa)002:419: sprul pa'i 'od zer mtha' yas par spro ba /
NK020(wa)002:420: yum gnam zhal dbyings kyi dbang phyug ma sngon mo dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa /
NK020(wa)002:421: rtsa zhal mthing ga he ru ka'i gsang ba'i rdo rje dang sbyor ba /
NK020(wa)002:422: g.yas zhal bzhi ljang dmar mthing ser yab kyi zhabs g.yas pa bzhi dang sbyor ba /
NK020(wa)002:423: g.yon zhal bzhi dmar ljang dkar dmar yab kyi zhabs g.yon pa bzhi dang sbyor ba /
NK020(wa)002:424: phyag dang po gnyis kyis rdo rje dang dung khrag /
NK020(wa)002:425: lhag ma g.yas pa brgyad na gnas kyi ma mo brgyad /
NK020(wa)002:426: g.yon pa brgyad na yul gyi phra men brgyan bsnams pa /
NK020(wa)002:427: gzig gi lpags pa'i sham thabs sogs khro mo'i chas kyis brgyan pa /
NK020(wa)002:428: zhabs bzhi bgrad pa'i stabs kyis stan la rol zhing /
NK020(wa)002:429: ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa /
NK020(wa)002:430: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams
NK020(wa)002:431: cad bcom ldan 'das kyi zhabs kyi gdan khri nas
NK020(wa)002:432: dbu'i gtsug tor man chad la rdzogs par snang ba'i
NK020(wa)002:433: bdag nyid chen por gyur pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:434: gnyis pa khrag 'thung drug cu rtsa bzhi bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)002:435: phyogs kyi re'u mig bzhi la rigs bzhi'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)002:436: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:437: badz+ra shwa ri kha mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:438: shar du rdo rje rgyal tshab ces bya ba'i zhe sdang rdo rje dkar po g.yas rdo rje /
NK020(wa)002:439: sarba ta th+aa ga ta rat+na ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:440: rat+na shwa ri kha mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:441: lhor rdo rje gung phur zhes bya ba'i nga rgyal rin chen sngon po rin po che /
NK020(wa)002:442: sarba ta th+aa ga ta pad+ma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aah+aa /
NK020(wa)002:443: pad+ma sha ri kha mum s+w+aah+aa /
NK020(wa)002:444: nub tu rdo rje king zhes bya ba'i 'dod chags pad+ma dkar po g.yas pad+ma /
NK020(wa)002:445: sarba ta th+aa ga ta karma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:446: karma shwa ri kha mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:447: byang du rdo rje las skyes zhes bya ba'i phrag dog sna tshogs pa ljang gu g.yas rgya gram /
NK020(wa)002:448: thams cad kyi g.yon b+han dmar 'dzin cing /
NK020(wa)002:449: zhe sdang rdo rje ma sogs rang mdog gi yum dril bu bsnams pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK020(wa)002:450: mtshams kyi re'u mig bzhi la cho 'phrul chen po'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)002:451: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa nu ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:452: sa nu shwa ri kha mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:453: shar lhor nam mkha'i dbang phyug sngo skya /
NK020(wa)002:454: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa ne ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:455: sa ne shwa ri kha mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:456: lho nub tu rnam grol sbyin pa dmar ser /
NK020(wa)002:457: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa no ma h+aa sh+r+ai
NK020(wa)002:458: he ru ka sa no shwa ri kha mum nub
NK020(wa)002:459: byang du rnam grol sgrogs pa dmar ljang /
NK020(wa)002:460: sarba ta th+aa ga ta wa ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai
NK020(wa)002:461: he ru ka wa ra shwa ri kha byang shar
NK020(wa)002:462: du thams cad grub pa ser skya /
NK020(wa)002:463: bzhi ka phyag g.yas gar bsgyur zhing /
NK020(wa)002:464: g.yon gyis yum nam mkha'i dbang mo sogs dang mdog can dril bu bsnams pa la 'khyud pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:466: ru dra rnam gsum dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:467: khrag 'thung dgu ru bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:468: bdud dang srin po'i bar chad kun bsgral nas //
NK020(wa)002:469: ye shes dgu ru lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:471: khams gsum sa dgu'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:472: yum chen dgu ru bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:473: ma bdud srin mo'i bar chad kun bsgral nas //
NK020(wa)002:474: thig le dgu ru lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:476: 'khor lo dang po rtsibs brgyad kyi phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhir dam tshig chen po'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)002:477: sarba ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra ga r+b+ha ma h+aa
NK020(wa)002:478: sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra gar+b+ha shwa ri kha mum
NK020(wa)002:479: s+w+aa h+aa / shar du rdo rje snying po dkar po g.yas rdo rje'i myu gu /
NK020(wa)002:480: sarba ta th+aa ga ta rat+na gar+b+ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK020(wa)002:481: rat+na gar+b+ha shwa ri kha mum lhor nor bu'i snying po ser po g.yas rin po che'i myu gu /
NK020(wa)002:482: sarba ta th+aa ga ta pad+ma gar+b+ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai
NK020(wa)002:483: he ru ka pad+ma gar+g+ha shwa ri kha mum nub
NK020(wa)002:484: tu pad+ma'i snying po dmar po g.yas pad+ma'i myu gu
NK020(wa)002:485: / sarba ta th+aa ga ta karma gar+b+ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:486: karma gar+b+ha shwa ri kha mum s+w+aah+aa /
NK020(wa)002:487: byang du bkod pa'i snying po ljang gu g.yas ral gri'i myu gu /
NK020(wa)002:488: de thams cad g.yon 'khyud stabs kyis yum rdo rje
NK020(wa)002:489: dbang phyug ma sogs rang mdog can dril bu bsnams
NK020(wa)002:492: rnam shes bzhi dang yul bzhi cir snang yang /
NK020(wa)002:493: dam tshig chen po bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:494: lha rtog gnyis med rtogs las mi 'da' ba'i //
NK020(wa)002:495: dam tshig chen po lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:497: 'khor lo rim pa gnyis pa'i phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhir tshad med pa'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)002:498: sarba ta th+aa ga ta mee tri gar+b+ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:499: mee tri gar+b+ha shwa ri kha mum h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:500: shar du byams pa'i snying po dkar po g.yas rdo rje /
NK020(wa)002:501: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ru gar+b+ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:502: k+aa ra gar+b+ha shwa ri kha mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:503: lhor snying rje'i snying po ser po g.yas rin chen /
NK020(wa)002:504: sarba ta th+aa ga ta lo ka gar+b+ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:505: lo ka gar+b+ha shwa ri kha mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:506: nub tu dga' ba'i snying po dmar po g.yas pad+ma /
NK020(wa)002:507: sarba ta th+aa ga ta bi du ma gar+b+ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:508: bi du ma gar+b+ha shwa ri kha mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:509: byang du btang snyoms kyi snying po ljang gu g.yas ral gri /
NK020(wa)002:510: de thams cad g.yon skyabs sbyin gyis yum bde ba'i
NK020(wa)002:511: dbang phyug ma sogs skyabs sbyin gyis dril bu bsnams
NK020(wa)002:514: dbang po bzhi dang dus bzhi cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:515: tshad med yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:516: tshad me rnam bzhi'i yon tan ma lus pa //
NK020(wa)002:517: ye shes chen por ma 'dres yongs rdzogs shog /
NK020(wa)002:519: 'bar ba'i phreng bas bcad pa'i phyir rol /
NK020(wa)002:520: 'khor rim pa gsum pa'i phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhir rol pa chen po'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)002:521: sarba ta th+aa ga ta yak+sha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he
NK020(wa)002:522: ru ka yak+sha shwa ri kha mum shar du yak+sha
NK020(wa)002:523: he ru ka smug nag rdo rje /
NK020(wa)002:524: sarba ta th+aa ga ta rak+sha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK020(wa)002:525: rak+sha shwa ri ka mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:526: lhor rak+sha he ru ka sngo nag be con //
NK020(wa)002:527: sarba ta th+aa ga ta bi shwa ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka bi sha shwa ri ka /
NK020(wa)002:528: nub tu bi sha he ru ka dmar nag pad+ma /
NK020(wa)002:529: sarba ta th+aa ga ta bi shwa ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK020(wa)002:530: bi shwa shwa ri ka byang du bi shwa he
NK020(wa)002:531: ru ka ljang nag phag gi mche bas mtshan pa'i
NK020(wa)002:532: ral gri / de thams cad g.yon b+hany+dza dmar gyis gang ba 'dzin pas /
NK020(wa)002:533: yum yak+sha shwa ri ka la sogs pa g.yas mche
NK020(wa)002:534: bas mtshan pa'i dril bu dang g.yon b+han dmar snams
NK020(wa)002:537: phrag dog sdang sems gti mug cir snang yang /
NK020(wa)002:538: khrag 'thung yab yum brgyad du bsgoms pa'i mthus /
NK020(wa)002:539: rnam bzhi dregs pa'i rgyu 'bras kun bsgral nas /
NK020(wa)002:540: dbyings dang ye shes rol pa'i don rtogs shog /
NK020(wa)002:542: 'khor lo rim pa bzhi pa'i phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhir 'jigs byed chen po'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)002:543: sarba ta th+aa ga ta te shwa ma h+aa sh+r+ai
NK020(wa)002:544: he ru ka te shwa shwa ri ka mum s+w+aa
NK020(wa)002:545: h+aa / shar du te sha he ru ka smug
NK020(wa)002:546: nag rdo rjes mtshan pa'i seng ge'i rgyal mtshan pa
NK020(wa)002:547: h+aa / kha gdengs pa / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ke shwa ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK020(wa)002:548: ke shwa shwa ri ka mum lhor ke sha he
NK020(wa)002:549: ru ka ser nag rin po ches mtshan pa'i stag
NK020(wa)002:550: gi rgyal mtshan kha gdengs pa /
NK020(wa)002:551: sarba ta th+aa ga ta pa shwa ma h+aa sh+r+ai
NK020(wa)002:552: he ru ka pa shwa shwa ri ka mum nub
NK020(wa)002:553: tu pa sha he ru ka dmar nag pad+mas mtshan
NK020(wa)002:554: pa'i spyang ki'i rgyal mtshan gdengs pa /
NK020(wa)002:555: sarba ta th+aa ga ta bi shwa ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:556: bi shwa shwa ri ka mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:557: byang du be sha he ru ka ljang nag ral
NK020(wa)002:558: gris mtshan pa'i dom gyi rgyal mtshan kha gdengs pa
NK020(wa)002:559: / de thams cad g.yon dung dmar 'dzin pas ke
NK020(wa)002:560: sha shwa ri ka la sogs pa la 'khyud cing
NK020(wa)002:561: / / yum rnams kyang phyag mtshan yab ltar las rgyal mtshan pa dril bus mtshan pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:563: gnyis 'dzin rtog pa'i sdug bsngal cir snang yang /
NK020(wa)002:564: 'jigs byed yab yum brgyad du bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK020(wa)002:565: gdug can ma lus sngangs shing 'jigs byas nas //
NK020(wa)002:566: sgrol sbyor bsdams myos las bzhi mthar phyin shog /
NK020(wa)002:568: 'khor lo rim pa lnga pa'i phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhir 'joms byed chen po'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)002:569: sarba ta th+aa ga ta trag shwa ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:570: trag shwa shwa ri ka mam s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:571: shar du trag sha he ru ka smug nag rdo rjes mtshan pa'i zhing dbyug /
NK020(wa)002:572: sarba ta th+aa ga ta hri shwa ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:573: hri shwa shwa ri ka s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:574: lhor hri sha he ru ka ser nag rin po ches mtshan pa'i zhing dbyug /
NK020(wa)002:575: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ka shwa ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:576: ka shwa shwa ri ka mum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK020(wa)002:577: nub tu ka sha he ru ka dmar nag pad+mas mtshan pa'i zhing dbyug /
NK020(wa)002:578: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ba ga sha ma h+aa
NK020(wa)002:579: sh+r+ai he ru ka ba ga shwa shwa ri ka
NK020(wa)002:580: byang du pa sha he ru ka ljang nag rgya
NK020(wa)002:581: gram gyis mtshan pa'i zhing dbyug /
NK020(wa)002:582: de thams cad g.yon dung dmar 'dzin pas trag sha
NK020(wa)002:583: shwa ri ka sogs yum rnams yab ltar las zhing
NK020(wa)002:584: dbyug la dril bu sgra sgrog pas mtshan pa bsnams
NK020(wa)002:587: ma rungs gdug pa'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:588: 'joms byed yab yum brgyad du bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK020(wa)002:589: gdug pa can rnams 'joms par byed pa yi //
NK020(wa)002:590: sgrol zhing stob pa'i phrin las mthar phyin shog /
NK020(wa)002:592: 'khor lo rim pa tha ma'i phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhir za byed chen po'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)002:593: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ru ti ma h+aa sh+r+ai
NK020(wa)002:594: he ru ka ru ti shwa ri ka shar du
NK020(wa)002:595: ru ti he ru ka smug nag g.yas pas snying
NK020(wa)002:596: za ba / sarba ta th+aa ga ta rak+ti ma
NK020(wa)002:597: h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka rak+ti shwa ri ka mum
NK020(wa)002:598: lhor rag ti he ru ka ser nag g.yas nang
NK020(wa)002:599: za ba / khrol za ba / sarba ta th+aa
NK020(wa)002:600: ga ta kh+aa hi ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka
NK020(wa)002:601: kh+aa hi shwa ri ka nub tu kh+aa hi he
NK020(wa)002:602: ru ka dmar nag g.yas ske khrag 'jib pa /
NK020(wa)002:603: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai
NK020(wa)002:604: he ru ka sa ha shwa ri ka mum byang
NK020(wa)002:605: du sa ha he ru ka ljang nag g.yas yan
NK020(wa)002:606: lag za ba / de thams cad g.yon dung dmar
NK020(wa)002:607: 'dzin pas yum ru ti shwa ri ka sogs g.yas
NK020(wa)002:608: dril bu 'khrol zhing g.yon b+ha ny+dza bsnams pa la
NK020(wa)002:609: lag za ba / 'khyud pa / lha tshogs de
NK020(wa)002:610: thams cad kyang 'bar ba'i gar dgu dang ldan zhing
NK020(wa)002:611: lag za ba / 'khyud pa / / dur khrod rol pa'i chas can /
NK020(wa)002:612: so so'i gdan la rol ba'o //
NK020(wa)002:614: chags sdang rmongs pa'i rtog pa cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:615: za byed yab yum brgyad du bsgom pa'i mthus //
NK020(wa)002:616: bsgral ba'i zhing rnams ma lus gnas ston nas //
NK020(wa)002:617: spong len med par spyod pa'i mthu thob shog /
NK020(wa)002:620: phyogs kyi re'u mig brgyad dang /
NK020(wa)002:621: 'khor lo dang po dang gnyis pa'i lha rnams zhi bar mdzad pa ltar na /
NK020(wa)002:622: rigs lnga dang sems dpa' yab yum tshang bas /
NK020(wa)002:623: steng khang zhi dkyil logs su ma bsgom kyang chad par mi 'gyur ram snyam mod /
NK020(wa)002:624: 'dir ni rgya bdun 'grel sogs su zhi ba yin
NK020(wa)002:625: pa'i gsal byed med cing bskyed sngags dang mtshan gyis
NK020(wa)002:626: kyang khro bo ston par ma zad /
NK020(wa)002:627: rtsa rgyud kyi rgyur gyi ting nge 'dzin gyi le'u las /
NK020(wa)002:628: spyan 'bar ba drug cu rtsa bzhi ni he ru ka yab yum drug cu rtsa bzhir gsal lo //
NK020(wa)002:629: zhes da bu nyer gcig la spyan gsum gsum ste
NK020(wa)002:630: re gsum spas spyan gcig bcas re bzhi dang sbyar
NK020(wa)002:631: ba'i lha thams cad he ru kar gsungs pa dang
NK020(wa)002:633: mdo chen kun 'dus rgyud ltar tshogs chen 'dus //
NK020(wa)002:634: a nu gtso ltar zhi 'og khro he ru //
NK020(wa)002:635: che mchog rgyal po badz+ra rgyal tshab ni //
NK020(wa)002:636: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar byas pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:637: yang 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad kyi lha rnams phyogs rtsibs la bkod nas /
NK020(wa)002:638: mtshams rtsibs rnams stong par 'jog pa ni rnal 'byor sa'i sgrol ma las /
NK020(wa)002:639: 'di dag ni 'khor lo'i rtsibs re re la go rim bzhin du dgod ces zer na /
NK020(wa)002:640: yong mtshams kyi 'khor lo ye shes kyi yul bas stong par bzhag ste /
NK020(wa)002:641: phyogs kyi 'khor lo rnams la thabs dang shes rab sbyor ba'i stangs stabs su bzhugs //
NK020(wa)002:642: zhes gsungs pa ltar bkod pa ste /
NK020(wa)002:643: thabs shes so sor 'god par 'dod na /
NK020(wa)002:644: phyogs rnams su yab dang mtshams la yum rnams spel te dgod do //
NK020(wa)002:645: gsum pa bka' nyan gyi 'khor rnams bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)002:646: gru chad kyi lha snam nang ma la gsang ba'i bu mo'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)002:647: badz+ra goo r+ai hah shar lho'i shar du mdzod ldan ma nag mo zhing dbyug dang b+han dmar /
NK020(wa)002:648: badz+ra tsoo ri hah lho nub kyi lhor chom rkun ma ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa /
NK020(wa)002:649: badz+ra pra mo he hah nub byang gi nub tu
NK020(wa)002:650: rab rmongs ma dmar mo chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan
NK020(wa)002:651: dang thod khrag / badz+ra be ta l+ai hah byang
NK020(wa)002:652: shar gyi byang du ro langs ma nag mo rdo
NK020(wa)002:654: badz+ra puk+ka s+ai hah shar lho'i lhor sbos mo dmar ser zhing chung gi rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK020(wa)002:655: badz+ra g+ha sma r+ai hah lho nub kyi nub tu
NK020(wa)002:656: drod mo ljang gu dung khrag rdo rjes dkrug pa
NK020(wa)002:657: / badz+ra sma sha n+ai hah nub byang gi byang
NK020(wa)002:658: du dur khrod ma mthing nag zhing chung gi glu
NK020(wa)002:659: / snying za ba / badz+ra tsan+da l+ai hah byang
NK020(wa)002:660: shar gyi shar du gtum mo ser mo zhing chung
NK020(wa)002:663: rnam shes brgyad kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:664: goo r+ai brgyad du bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:665: yul la mngon par rtog pa kun bcom nas //
NK020(wa)002:666: rnam par rtog pa'i 'du shes med par shog /
NK020(wa)002:668: gru chad kyi lha snam phya ma la dga' ba'i bu mo'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)002:670: shar lho'i shar du seng gdong ser mo ro za zhing lag gnyis thugs kar bsnol ba /
NK020(wa)002:671: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kh+ai he /
NK020(wa)002:672: lho nub kyi lho stag gdong ma dmar mo lag gnyis mthur du bsnol ba /
NK020(wa)002:673: badz+ra sh+r+ai g+aa la mu kh+ai he /
NK020(wa)002:674: nub byang gi nub tu wa gdong ma nag mo zhing chung lces ldag pa /
NK020(wa)002:675: badz+ra shwa n+aa mu kh+ai he /
NK020(wa)002:676: byang shar gyi byang du khyi gdong ma mthing nag zhing gi khog pa 'dral ba /
NK020(wa)002:677: badz+ra g+h+ri d+d+ha mu kh+ai he /
NK020(wa)002:678: shar lho'i lhor rgod gdong ma dmar mo zhing gi rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK020(wa)002:680: lho nub kyi nub tu dur bya'i gdong ma dmar mo bam ro phrag bar 'khur ba /
NK020(wa)002:681: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kh+ai he /
NK020(wa)002:682: nub byang gi byang du khwa gdong ma nag mo ral gri dang b+han dmar /
NK020(wa)002:683: badz+ra u l+au k+aa mu kh+ai he /
NK020(wa)002:684: byang shar gyi shar du 'ug gdong ma mthing ga rdo rje'i dbyug pa 'dzin pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:686: dur khrod brgyad kyi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:687: phra men brgyad du bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:688: mtshan mar snang ba'i dngos po kun bral nas //
NK020(wa)002:689: rnam par rtog pa'i bar chad med par shog /
NK020(wa)002:693: shin tu gsod pa chen po'i 'khor khro bo bcu
NK020(wa)002:694: rang rang gi za byed mche ba can gyi gdong
NK020(wa)002:696: sprul pa khra thabs nyi shu dang bcas pa'i steng 'og gi khro bo shar nub dang /
NK020(wa)002:697: mtshams kyi khro bo rnams rang gnas /
NK020(wa)002:698: phyogs kyi khro bo bzhi po shar stod la sogs
NK020(wa)002:699: pa'i phyogs kyi sgo dang po rnams su bzhugs pa'o
NK020(wa)002:701: rus mgo tshigs mgo'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:702: khro bcu yab yum za gsod bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK020(wa)002:703: khams gsum gdug pa ma lus kun bsgral nas //
NK020(wa)002:704: sangs rgyas phrin las lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:706: khyams de nyid la ma mo brgyad dang ging bco brgyad kyang bzhugs te /
NK020(wa)002:707: ma ma dun b+h+yo brgyad kyis /
NK020(wa)002:711: rdo rje kun bzang ma dang /
NK020(wa)002:712: rdo rje ye shes mchog dang /
NK020(wa)002:713: rdo rje dpung sgrol ma dang /
NK020(wa)002:715: rdo rje srog gcod ma dang brgyad phyogs rer gnyis gnyis so //
NK020(wa)002:717: sha khrag rtsa yi dngos po cir snang yang /
NK020(wa)002:718: ma mo brgyad du bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:719: tshe srog gnod pa'i bar chad kun bsgral nas //
NK020(wa)002:720: nyin mtshan rtag tu thams cad skyob par shog /
NK020(wa)002:722: kim ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK020(wa)002:724: rdo rje chags chen dang rdo rje gnod sbyin dang /
NK020(wa)002:732: de dag gi sbyor ba'i yul khams gsum dbugs 'gengs chen mo dang /
NK020(wa)002:737: rna nyan phra ma mkhan dang /
NK020(wa)002:738: rbod gtong len par byed ma dang /
NK020(wa)002:739: snying rjes sgrol ba chen mo dang /
NK020(wa)002:740: phyag tshang mnyes byed chen mo dang /
NK020(wa)002:741: bco brgyad po shar nub tu lnga lnga dang lho byang du bzhi bzhi'o //
NK020(wa)002:743: gur rtsibs bco brgyad dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:744: ging chen bco brgyad bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:745: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu ma lus kun bsgral nas //
NK020(wa)002:746: sangs rgyas zhing khams yongs su dag par shog /
NK020(wa)002:748: shar smad la sogs pa'i phyogs bzhi'i sgo gnyis pa rnams su shin tu gus pa'i 'khor /
NK020(wa)002:749: badz+ra +aa r+ya te dza te nga dzah shar sgor
NK020(wa)002:750: rta gdong ma dkar mo lcags kyu dang thod khrag
NK020(wa)002:752: lhor sgor phag gdong ma ser mo zhags pa badz+ra lo ka bam /
NK020(wa)002:753: nub sgor spre'u gdong ma dmar mo lcags sgrog badz+ra
NK020(wa)002:754: b+hasmi pa la ya ba tu hoh byang sgor spyang
NK020(wa)002:755: gdong ma ljang gu dril bu dang thod khrag bsnams
NK020(wa)002:757: chu bo bzhi yi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:758: sgo ma bzhi ru bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:759: tshad med bzhi ru rdzogs pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)002:760: phrin las rnam bzhi 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK020(wa)002:765: shar du mkha' 'gro dga' byed ma /
NK020(wa)002:772: bong bu'i gdong ma dang bzhi /
NK020(wa)002:781: shar lhor bya rgod gdong ma /
NK020(wa)002:784: sna tshogs mchog gi gzugs can ma dang bzhi /
NK020(wa)002:785: lho nub tu bong bu'i gdong ma /
NK020(wa)002:792: lce spyang 'khor can ma dang bzhi /
NK020(wa)002:793: byang shar du bum sna ma /
NK020(wa)002:796: d+ha sha g+r+ai ba dang bzhi ste /
NK020(wa)002:797: phyogs mtshams kyi bzhi bzhi rigs bsdus pas mkha' 'gro brgyad dang /
NK020(wa)002:798: de dag rdzu 'phrul gyis 'gro ba'i sprul pa mdzes
NK020(wa)002:799: sdug 'od 'bar sogs shugs 'gro brgyad dang bcas pa'o
NK020(wa)002:801: so dang rus pa'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:802: mkha' 'gro shugs 'gro bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:803: bar du gcod pa ma lus kun bsgral nas //
NK020(wa)002:804: sgrub pa'i bar chad ming yang med par shog /
NK020(wa)002:806: phyogs kyi sgo dang po bzhir /
NK020(wa)002:807: sh+r+ai badz+ra mung+ga ra mu kha shwa ra y+aa ya
NK020(wa)002:808: na mah shar sgor dkar mo mig gcig rgyas 'debs
NK020(wa)002:809: ma rdo rje / sh+r+ai badz+ra rag ma shwa ra
NK020(wa)002:810: y+aa ya na mah lho sgor ser mo las mkhan
NK020(wa)002:812: sh+r+ai badz+ra kha t+w+aam ka pra dz+wa la y+aa ya
NK020(wa)002:813: na mah nub sgor dmar mo za byed dbang sdud
NK020(wa)002:814: ma rgyal mtshan / sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+de pra dz+wa la
NK020(wa)002:815: y+aa ya na mah byang sgor nag mo ral gcig
NK020(wa)002:816: rmongs byed ma dril bu bsnams pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:818: 'byung ba bzhi yi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:819: gsang ba'i yum bzhi bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:820: chos nyid dwangs snyigs med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)002:821: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK020(wa)002:825: shar sgor gling bzhi mgyogs ma /
NK020(wa)002:826: lho sgor mkha' la khyung lding ma //
NK020(wa)002:827: nub sgor dmar mo g.yag thod ma /
NK020(wa)002:828: byang sgor nag mo sder chen mo dang bzhi'o //
NK020(wa)002:829: h+aum sha khrag rtsa yi dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:830: sring mo bzhi ru bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:831: tshe srog gnod pa'i bar chad kun bsgral nas //
NK020(wa)002:832: nyin mtshan rtag tu thams cad skyob par shog /
NK020(wa)002:836: khyab byed chen mo khyung gi mgo dang /
NK020(wa)002:837: gsod byed chen mo sre mong mgo dang /
NK020(wa)002:838: mgyogs ma snyegs byed khra'i mgo dang /
NK020(wa)002:840: myos byed smig bu'i mgo dang /
NK020(wa)002:841: rkun mo byi la'i mgo dang /
NK020(wa)002:842: gdug byed sbrul gyi mgo dang /
NK020(wa)002:843: sgrin byed pha wang gi mgo can brgyad po phyogs dang mtshams la bzhugs shing /
NK020(wa)002:844: phyogs kyi sgo gnyis gnyis te brgyad la /
NK020(wa)002:848: seng ge dang pha wang gi gdong can brgyad do //
NK020(wa)002:849: h+aum sna tshogs rtog pa'i snang ba cir snang yang /
NK020(wa)002:850: rdo rje phra men bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)002:851: srid gsum gdug pa'i tshogs rnams kun bsgral nas /
NK020(wa)002:852: mngon spyod drag po'i phrin las lhun grub shog /
NK020(wa)002:854: khyams de nyid kyi phra men brgyad po re re'i g.yon phyogs su /
NK020(wa)002:855: badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tu rta ra phata rak+mo h+aum brgyad kyis /
NK020(wa)002:856: shar du 'bar ma nyi zer can dmar mo nyi zer gyi zhags pa /
NK020(wa)002:857: shar lhor me khyer glog phreng ma dmar mo glog zhags /
NK020(wa)002:858: lhor skar mda' 'phen sngon mo mdung thung dang skar mda' 'phen pa /
NK020(wa)002:859: lho nub tu srin mo rlung nag ral gri'i skra can sngon mo khyung khra 'gyed pa /
NK020(wa)002:860: nub tu klu mo lce 'bebs ma dkar mo thog 'bebs pa /
NK020(wa)002:861: nub byang du gnod sbyin khyung thogs ma sngon mo khyung 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)002:862: byang du ba lang sna glang po'i gdong can sngo nag thog ser 'bebs pa /
NK020(wa)002:863: byang shar du mig 'byin snying sreg ma thal kar ral gri 'phyar ba'o //
NK020(wa)002:864: h+aum phyogs mtshams brgyad kyi dngos po cir snang yang /
NK020(wa)002:865: spor ma brgyad du bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:866: snang srid sde brgyad bar chad kun bsal nas //
NK020(wa)002:867: 'jig rten bar chad ming yang med par shog /
NK020(wa)002:871: rdo rje gnod sbyin ma dza gad kyis bkang ba'i
NK020(wa)002:872: byi ru la sogs pa'i phor pa thogs pa brgyad
NK020(wa)002:873: phyogs mtshams dang / sgor srid mo rak+tasa bkang ba'i gzhong pa thogs pa brgyad do //
NK020(wa)002:875: 'jig rten bskyed sdud dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:876: gnod sbyin srin mo bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:877: sman gyis gso zhing chags pas bsdus byas nas //
NK020(wa)002:878: thabs shes bde bas kun tu khyab par shog /
NK020(wa)002:888: srin mo smug nag g.yag gdong rtse gsum 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)002:889: tshangs ma dmar ser sbrul gdong rtse lnga dang b+han dmar /
NK020(wa)002:890: 'khrug mo dmar ser gzig gdong dbyug to dang snying /
NK020(wa)002:891: khyab 'jug ma ser mo pha wam gdong can 'khor lo dang gun+d+he /
NK020(wa)002:892: dbang mo dmar skya dred gdong bam dbyug /
NK020(wa)002:893: brgya byin ma dkar dmar sre mong mgo can thod khrag 'dzin pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:901: zhi ba dmar mo dom mgo dung dmar dang rgyu zhags /
NK020(wa)002:902: bdud rtsi ma sngon mo chu srin mgo can bum pa /
NK020(wa)002:903: zhi ba ma sngo skya sdig pa'i mgo can thod pa bam ril dang ti ra /
NK020(wa)002:904: be con ma nag mo khra mgo can thod rlon /
NK020(wa)002:905: srin mo dmar nag wa gdong zhing gi rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK020(wa)002:906: za byed nag mo stag mgo bam snying 'byin pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:909: e ka tsa ri n+ai b+h+yo /
NK020(wa)002:914: dga' byed dmar mo rgod gdong ral gri dang 'khor lo /
NK020(wa)002:915: khrag 'thung ma dmar nag rta gdong rdo rje'i dbyug pa dang dung dmar /
NK020(wa)002:916: rdo rje ser mo khyung gdong rdo rje dang b+han dmar /
NK020(wa)002:917: 'dod pa dmar ser khyi gdong zhing chen za ba /
NK020(wa)002:918: nor srung dkar dmar pu shud mgo can pad+ma /
NK020(wa)002:919: rlung mo dmar skya sha ba'i mgo can bam ro za ba'o //
NK020(wa)002:920: ma h+aa m+aa ra na badz+ra b+h+yo /
NK020(wa)002:927: gsod byed ma ljang nag spyang gdong bam chen dang rnge'u chung /
NK020(wa)002:928: me mo ljang dmar skyin gdong me sgron dang rgyu ma /
NK020(wa)002:929: phag mo ljang ser phag gdong rtse gsum 'dzin pa /
NK020(wa)002:930: rgan byed ljang sngon khra mgo can rgyu ma 'dren cing dung khrag 'thor ba /
NK020(wa)002:931: sna chen ljang dmar glang po'i gdon can bam ro /
NK020(wa)002:932: chu lha ma ljang nag sbrul gdong dung dmar dang sbrul zhags 'dzin pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:933: badz+ra ma h+aa k+aa li b+h+yo /
NK020(wa)002:937: shar sgor nag mo chen mo khu byug mgo can lcags kyu /
NK020(wa)002:938: lho sgor ra gdong sngon mo rgyu zhags /
NK020(wa)002:939: nub sgor seng gdong dmar mo lcags sgrog /
NK020(wa)002:940: byang sgor skya ka'i mgo can ljang nag dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:942: sgal tshigs nyer brgyad dngos po cir snang yang /
NK020(wa)002:943: dbang phyug nyer brgyad bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK020(wa)002:944: rnam par rtog pa'i bar chad kun bsal nas /
NK020(wa)002:945: bar chad rkyen gyi sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK020(wa)002:947: phyogs kyi ma drug gi phyi rol tu /
NK020(wa)002:948: b+ha na b+ha na ang+ku sha dzah ha la ha la p+aa sha h+aum /
NK020(wa)002:950: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+de hoh kro d+ha kro d+h+ai h+aum /
NK020(wa)002:953: shar smad du mi mo gser gyi mdun zhu can dang /
NK020(wa)002:954: shar lhor dung gi sbyang mo mgo dgu ma /
NK020(wa)002:955: lhor mi mo stag gi tshul can /
NK020(wa)002:956: lho nub na lcags kyi spyang mo mgo dgu ma /
NK020(wa)002:957: nub stod du mi mo dung gi tshul mchu can /
NK020(wa)002:958: nub byang na zangs kyi spyang mo mgo dgu ma /
NK020(wa)002:959: byang na ma mo lcags kyi mchu can ma /
NK020(wa)002:960: byang shar na g.yu spyang mgo dgu ma /
NK020(wa)002:961: shar stod na steng gi pho nya lcags kyi bya khra chen mo /
NK020(wa)002:962: nub smad du 'og gi pho nya lcags kyu byi ba chen mo ste /
NK020(wa)002:963: pho nya'i gtso mo bcu 'khor dang bcas pa sum brgya drug cu rnams bzhugs par gyur /
NK020(wa)002:965: lus bcud rtsa mdud dngos po cir snang yang /
NK020(wa)002:966: pho nya sum brgya drug cu bsgoms pa'i mthus /
NK020(wa)002:967: dam tshig nyams dang dgra bgegs kun bsgral nas /
NK020(wa)002:968: gnod pa'i bar chad ming yang med par shog /
NK020(wa)002:970: bzhi pa rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)002:971: ma h+aa gu ru sh+aa ri ram g+ai li h+aum /
NK020(wa)002:972: rgyu'i rta babs kyi phyi rol khor yug zlum po
NK020(wa)002:973: la dam pa'i rigs can dra ma lnga la sogs
NK020(wa)002:974: pa nas 'khor lo'i dbang phyug rtsa ba'i bla ma'i
NK020(wa)002:975: bar du byon pa'i rgya bod kyi rig 'dzin /
NK020(wa)002:980: rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rtsal rnal 'byor gyi sa la
NK020(wa)002:981: bzhugs pa'i dus gsum gyi rig 'dzin bla ma bye
NK020(wa)002:982: ba sa ya'i tshogs rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK020(wa)002:984: rig 'dzin bla ma byin rlabs ldan pa'i tshogs //
NK020(wa)002:985: brgyud pa gsum ldan bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:986: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi dgongs pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)002:987: rgyud lung man ngag lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:989: lnga pa zhar byung mgron thabs kyi lha bskyed pa ni /
NK020(wa)002:990: rta babs kyi sgor rdo rje kham rgya ma drug dang /
NK020(wa)002:992: yang sprul nag mo mche gshog can dang /
NK020(wa)002:994: sgrol byed la sogs pa phyag brnyan 'bum phrag mtha'
NK020(wa)002:995: yas pa'i tshogs bsam gyis mi khyab pas kun tu
NK020(wa)002:996: khyab cing gang bar bsam mo //
NK020(wa)002:997: de ltar dbyings rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi rang
NK020(wa)002:998: rtsal 'gag med ye shes kyi 'khor lo phrin las
NK020(wa)002:999: rnam pa bzhi'i sgyu 'phrul gyi rol pa sems can
NK020(wa)002:1000: thams cad kyi mos pa dang /
NK020(wa)002:1002: dbang po'i khyad par ji lta ba dang 'tshams par
NK020(wa)002:1003: 'char ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi sprin chen por rtag tu
NK020(wa)002:1005: gnyis pa dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK020(wa)002:1006: rang gi spyi bo'i gnas lngar de bzhin gshegs pa
NK020(wa)002:1007: rigs lnga yab yum snyoms par zhugs pa'i rjes chags
NK020(wa)002:1008: kyi mes zhu ba'i ye shes lnga'i chu rgyun gyis
NK020(wa)002:1010: rigs lnga'i dbang rgya spyi bo'i gnas lngar 'jog cing /
NK020(wa)002:1011: ma h+aa shu nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK020(wa)002:1012: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na ma h+aa sa ma
NK020(wa)002:1013: t+aa ma h+aa pra t+ya be k+sha na ma h+aa
NK020(wa)002:1014: kri t+ya nush+sh+aa na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa
NK020(wa)002:1016: zhes dbang sngags rnams rim par brjod la /
NK020(wa)002:1017: dbang bskur bas nyon mongs pa lnga'i dri ma sbyangs /
NK020(wa)002:1018: phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su gnas sgyur /
NK020(wa)002:1019: chu lhag ma spyi bor brtan po yongs su gyur
NK020(wa)002:1020: pa las de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lngas dbu brgyan
NK020(wa)002:1021: par bsam mo // byin gyis rlob pa ni /
NK020(wa)002:1022: spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i dkar po /
NK020(wa)002:1023: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK020(wa)002:1024: sku rdo rje lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK020(wa)002:1026: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK020(wa)002:1027: yongs su gyur pa las rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo 'dzin pas rgyas btab par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)002:1028: rdo rje'i phyag rgya spyi bor gtugs la /
NK020(wa)002:1029: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK020(wa)002:1030: mgrin par pad+ma la gnas pa'i +aah dmar po /
NK020(wa)002:1031: de'i 'od zer gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK020(wa)002:1032: gsung rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK020(wa)002:1034: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung dang gnyis su med par gyur //
NK020(wa)002:1035: +aahyongasa su gyur pa las snang mtha' dmar po pad+ma 'dzin pas rgyas btab par bsam zhing /
NK020(wa)002:1036: rdo rje'i phyag rgya mgrin par /
NK020(wa)002:1037: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aa t+ma ko&a ham /
NK020(wa)002:1038: snying gar nyi ma la gnas pa'i h+aum sngon po /
NK020(wa)002:1039: de'i 'od zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK020(wa)002:1040: thugs rdo rje'i lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK020(wa)002:1042: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs dang gnyis su med par gyur /
NK020(wa)002:1043: h+aum yongs su gyur pa las mi bskyod pa sngon
NK020(wa)002:1044: po rdo rje 'dzin pas rgyas btab par bsam zhing
NK020(wa)002:1045: / rdo rje'i phyag rgya snying gar /
NK020(wa)002:1046: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK020(wa)002:1048: sku gsung thugs rdo rje gsum du nga rgyal byas la /
NK020(wa)002:1050: lus ngag yid gsum dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:1051: dbang bskur byin gyis brlab pa'i nus mthu yis //
NK020(wa)002:1052: nyon mongs dngos po ma lus kun byang nas //
NK020(wa)002:1053: sku dang ye shes lhun gyi grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:1055: gsum pa las kyi rim pa'i ting nge 'dzin la /
NK020(wa)002:1056: ye shes kyi 'khor lo spyan drang zhing bstim pa /
NK020(wa)002:1063: ga go na'i rgya bcings te /
NK020(wa)002:1064: rang gi snying ga'i 'od dang rol pa chen po'i
NK020(wa)002:1065: glu bskul bas nam mkha' gang ba'i de bzhin gshegs
NK020(wa)002:1066: pa thams cad bde ba chen po'i ngang las cho
NK020(wa)002:1067: 'phrul gyi rnam rol zhi khro rab 'byams rgyal ba'i
NK020(wa)002:1068: dkyil 'khor chen por sad par bsam la /
NK020(wa)002:1070: tshogs chen gnyis rdzogs thugs dam dbyings kyi lha //
NK020(wa)002:1071: longs spyod rdzogs mdzad rol pa chen po'i sku //
NK020(wa)002:1072: rdo rje sems dpa' skal bzang dpal khyod bdag /
NK020(wa)002:1073: thabs kyi rol pas bde chen dbyings nas bzhengs //
NK020(wa)002:1074: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah ru lu ru lu h+aum /
NK020(wa)002:1075: zhes snyan gsan dbab pas 'byon ma rag par bsam la /
NK020(wa)002:1077: chos sku rig pa rang snang ba //
NK020(wa)002:1078: rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs dang //
NK020(wa)002:1079: khams gsum ma lus 'dul ba yi //
NK020(wa)002:1081: rdo rje 'chang gral rim brnyes pa'i //
NK020(wa)002:1083: smon lam dam tshig tshul bzhin du //
NK020(wa)002:1084: gnas 'dir ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK020(wa)002:1085: dzahh+aum bam hoh e h+ye hi /
NK020(wa)002:1086: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo dzah dzah zhes pas
NK020(wa)002:1087: dam tshig gi 'khor lo dang nye bar spyan drangs
NK020(wa)002:1088: te // thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK020(wa)002:1089: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan yang 'dren //
NK020(wa)002:1090: lcags sgrog bka' yi pho nya gnas bskyod la //
NK020(wa)002:1091: bde gshegs bzhugs shing rnam grol dgyes pa bskyed //
NK020(wa)002:1092: dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra sa ma ya mu dra a /
NK020(wa)002:1093: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka ti sh+tha sa ma ya lhan /
NK020(wa)002:1094: zhes pas rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor ting nge 'dzin
NK020(wa)002:1095: gyi dkyil 'khor la chu la chu bzhag pa ltar
NK020(wa)002:1096: dbyer med du bstim nas brtan par bzhugs su gsol
NK020(wa)002:1098: sangs rgyas sems can dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:1099: bde gshegs spyan drangs bstim pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:1100: ye nas gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)002:1101: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:1103: gnyis pa phyag bya ba ni /
NK020(wa)002:1105: rdo rje rkang lag mdzes pa'i gar //
NK020(wa)002:1106: nam mkha'i rdul snyed rab sprul te //
NK020(wa)002:1109: e ma'o ngo mtshar ya mtshan gyi //
NK020(wa)002:1111: ngo mtshar kun gyi bdag po mchog /
NK020(wa)002:1112: rdo rje rgyal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK020(wa)002:1113: byang chub sems dang dkyil 'khor dang //
NK020(wa)002:1114: phyag rgya bsnyen sgrub sgrub pa dang //
NK020(wa)002:1115: sdom dang brtul zhugs las rnams dang //
NK020(wa)002:1116: nan tur bdag po khyod la 'dud //
NK020(wa)002:1117: khyod ni sangs rgyas kun gyi yab //
NK020(wa)002:1118: de bzhin rgyal ba'i snying por gyur //
NK020(wa)002:1119: bdag cag rnams kyi brten pa'i gnas //
NK020(wa)002:1121: a ti p+au hoh pra ti p+au hoh zhes pas
NK020(wa)002:1122: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i ngang du
NK020(wa)002:1123: rtogs pa nyid 'dres pa nan tan gyi phyag yin
NK020(wa)002:1124: la / de'i phyir phyag mchod bya bar mi dmigs kyang /
NK020(wa)002:1126: bdag gi sprul pa'i mchod sprin dang /
NK020(wa)002:1127: nam mkha' gang ba'i ye shes kyi lha tshogs thams
NK020(wa)002:1128: cad lha la lha rol pa'i tshul gyis rol par
NK020(wa)002:1129: bsam pa ste / phyag mchod kyi gnas skabs thams cad la shes par bya'o //
NK020(wa)002:1131: bdag dang gzhan du khyad par cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:1132: dkyil 'khor lha la phyag btsal byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:1133: ye nas 'dres pa chen po'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)002:1134: gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:1136: gsum pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK020(wa)002:1138: bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK020(wa)002:1139: de 'dra kho nar bdag gyur cig /
NK020(wa)002:1140: spyod pa rmad byung bsam yas pa //
NK020(wa)002:1141: 'gro la phan phyir bdag gis spyad //
NK020(wa)002:1142: byang chub sems mchog dam pa dang //
NK020(wa)002:1143: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya 'di //
NK020(wa)002:1144: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong na //
NK020(wa)002:1145: rdo rje rgyal pos byin rlabs mdzod //
NK020(wa)002:1147: sangs rgyas mdzad dka' bdag gis bsgrubs //
NK020(wa)002:1148: byang chub spyod dka' bdag gi spyad //
NK020(wa)002:1150: bdag cag bsam pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK020(wa)002:1153: sgrub pa'i phrin las gsum gyi don la lhag pa'i bsam pa rtse gcig par dam bcas la /
NK020(wa)002:1155: 'gro drug sems can sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:1156: dam bca' rnam gsum byas pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:1157: bsam pa mtha' ru phyin pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK020(wa)002:1158: bdag gzhan gnyis ka'i don rnams mthar phyin shog /
NK020(wa)002:1160: gnyis pa mchod pa la bcu gcig las /
NK020(wa)002:1161: dang po phyag rgya'i mchod pa ni /
NK020(wa)002:1162: lag pa g.yas kyi sor mo'i bre kha lnga la /
NK020(wa)002:1165: gung mdzub dbang mo chung ngu sbom po rnams la /
NK020(wa)002:1167: g.yon gyi sor mo'i bre kha lnga la /
NK020(wa)002:1170: gung mdzub dbang mo chung ngu sbom po rnams la /
NK020(wa)002:1171: l+aam m+aum m+aam p+aam t+aam rnams kyis mtshan par gyur /
NK020(wa)002:1172: rnal 'byor mchog gi lag gnyis la /
NK020(wa)002:1174: a dang ma gnyis gsal bzhag ste /
NK020(wa)002:1175: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med sbyar /
NK020(wa)002:1178: dang m+aum gnyis rtse sprad la //
NK020(wa)002:1179: de bzhin h+aum dang l+aam du sbyar /
NK020(wa)002:1180: h+aa dang p+aam yang de bzhin te /
NK020(wa)002:1181: +aam dang t+aam du sbyar ba las /
NK020(wa)002:1182: rgyab sbyar s+w+aa dang m+aam sgreng ba //
NK020(wa)002:1183: 'di ni yab kyi spyi rgya yin //
NK020(wa)002:1185: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK020(wa)002:1186: mchod bzhes dam skongs dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)002:1187: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum ma h+aa mu dra h'u /
NK020(wa)002:1188: zhes mdun du bsgyur nas g.yon du dgrol /
NK020(wa)002:1189: lag pa thal mo sbyar ba las //
NK020(wa)002:1190: dang m+aum sbyar h+aum dang ni //
NK020(wa)002:1191: l+aam sbyar s+w+aa dang p+aam du sbyar //
NK020(wa)002:1192: +aam dang m+aam sbyar h+aa t+aam sgreng //
NK020(wa)002:1193: yum gyi spyi rgya yin par bshad /
NK020(wa)002:1195: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK020(wa)002:1197: ru lu ru lu zhes pas mdun du bsgyur nas g.yas su dgrol /
NK020(wa)002:1199: mnyam pa'i tshul du gnas pa la //
NK020(wa)002:1200: ma yi steng du a nyid bzhag /
NK020(wa)002:1201: bya ba thams cad bral ba'i rgya //
NK020(wa)002:1203: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK020(wa)002:1204: mchod bzhes dam skongs ru lu ru lu a dang ma yi 'bru bcu rnams //
NK020(wa)002:1208: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK020(wa)002:1209: mchod bzhed dam skongs ru lu ru lu a dang mi yi 'bru bcu rnams //
NK020(wa)002:1210: so sor bcangs te myu gur bya //
NK020(wa)002:1211: shin tu gtod de kun tu bsgyur //
NK020(wa)002:1213: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK020(wa)002:1214: mchod bzhes dam skongs ru lu ru lu ma yi sbyin pa gtong tshul la //
NK020(wa)002:1215: a yis thams cad skyob byed pa //
NK020(wa)002:1216: 'di ni tshad med chen po yi //
NK020(wa)002:1217: kun la snyoms pa'i phyag rgya yin //
NK020(wa)002:1218: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK020(wa)002:1219: mchod bzhes dam skongs ru lu ru lu ma nyid khrag rnams 'phrog pa'i snod //
NK020(wa)002:1220: a nyid so phreng mche bar sbyar //
NK020(wa)002:1221: 'di ni thams cad rol pa yi //
NK020(wa)002:1222: 'jigs tshul ston pa'i phyag rgya yin //
NK020(wa)002:1223: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK020(wa)002:1224: mchod bzhes dam skongs ru lu ru lu /
NK020(wa)002:1225: a dang ma gnyis rting sbyar te //
NK020(wa)002:1226: so phreng mche ba'i tshul gyis ni //
NK020(wa)002:1227: shin tu kha glal pa yi tshul //
NK020(wa)002:1229: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK020(wa)002:1230: mchod bzhes dam skongs ru lu ru lu ma yis bzung ste 'then nas ni //
NK020(wa)002:1231: a yis gdengs shing 'doms byed pa //
NK020(wa)002:1232: 'joms byed chen po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK020(wa)002:1233: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK020(wa)002:1234: mchod bzhes dam skongs ru lu ma dang a yis mgo mjug nas //
NK020(wa)002:1235: bzung ba'i tshul du byas nas ni /
NK020(wa)002:1237: za byed chen po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK020(wa)002:1238: 'bar ba'i gdan la mchod bzhes ru lu a dang ma yi shes rab las //
NK020(wa)002:1239: g.yas g.yon tshul gyis bsgyur byas te //
NK020(wa)002:1240: so so ji ltar yin thabs sbyar //
NK020(wa)002:1241: khrag 'thung rnams kyi yum gyi rgya //
NK020(wa)002:1242: 'bar ba'i gdan la mchod bzhes ru lu gnas ma brgyad kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK020(wa)002:1243: goo r+ai b+han dmar zhing dbyug sngo //
NK020(wa)002:1244: tsoo r+ai mda' gzhu 'gengs ma ser //
NK020(wa)002:1245: pra mo chu srin rgyal mtshan dmar //
NK020(wa)002:1246: be ta byis za rdor 'phyar nag /
NK020(wa)002:1249: sma sha mthing nag byis snying za //
NK020(wa)002:1251: 'bar ba'i gdan la mchod bzhes ru lu yul ma brgyad kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK020(wa)002:1252: sid+ha kha ro snol ser seng /
NK020(wa)002:1253: b+y+aa g+h+ri gnas lta bsnol mar stag /
NK020(wa)002:1254: sh+ri g+aal nag mo byis ldag wa //
NK020(wa)002:1255: shwa n+aa 'dral lta mthing ga spyang //
NK020(wa)002:1257: kang+ka kang phrag snar mgo ring //
NK020(wa)002:1258: k+aa ka kha ro b+han gri nag /
NK020(wa)002:1259: u l+au lcags kyu mthing tshogs 'ug /
NK020(wa)002:1260: 'bar ba'i gdan la mchod bzhes ru lu khro bcu'i spyi rgya /
NK020(wa)002:1261: dpal bo gdan la bzhengs nas ni //
NK020(wa)002:1262: phyogs mtshams kun tu bltas byas nas //
NK020(wa)002:1263: shin tu 'gying zhing brjid par bya //
NK020(wa)002:1264: a dang ma yi 'bru rnams ni //
NK020(wa)002:1265: so sor bsdams nas dkur brten bya //
NK020(wa)002:1266: 'di ni khro bo spyi yi rgya //
NK020(wa)002:1267: 'bar ba'i mchod ru lu sgo ma bzhi yi phyag rgya ni //
NK020(wa)002:1268: rta gdong sngon mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK020(wa)002:1269: phag gdong nag mo mche zhags can //
NK020(wa)002:1270: seng gdong dmar mo lcags sgrog sdom //
NK020(wa)002:1272: 'bar ba'i mchod ru lu 'jig rten 'das dang ma 'das pa'i //
NK020(wa)002:1273: ye shes thob par bya ba'i phyir //
NK020(wa)002:1274: ma mo rnams kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK020(wa)002:1275: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK020(wa)002:1276: tshangs ma dmar ser pad+ma bsnams //
NK020(wa)002:1277: lha chen dkar ljang tri shu la //
NK020(wa)002:1279: gzhon nu dmar mo mdung thung 'phen //
NK020(wa)002:1280: brgya byin dkar mo in+d+ra gdengs //
NK020(wa)002:1282: bdud rtsi dmar mo pad+ma bsnams //
NK020(wa)002:1283: zla ba dkar mo pun+da ri //
NK020(wa)002:1284: be con ljang nag dbyug tho 'phyar //
NK020(wa)002:1285: srin mo dmar mo dung khrag 'thung //
NK020(wa)002:1286: za ba ljang nag ba su 'dren //
NK020(wa)002:1287: dga' ba dkar mo ka tar 'phyar //
NK020(wa)002:1288: stobs chen dkar mo gshol mda' 'dzin //
NK020(wa)002:1289: rdo rje ser mo spu gris gcod //
NK020(wa)002:1291: nor srung dkar mo bum pa 'dzin //
NK020(wa)002:1292: rlung lha sngon mo ba dan 'phyar //
NK020(wa)002:1293: gsod byed dkar mo ral gri 'dzin //
NK020(wa)002:1294: me mo dmar mo gsal shing 'phyar //
NK020(wa)002:1295: phag gdong nag mo mche zhags can //
NK020(wa)002:1296: rgan byed dmar mo zhing chung za //
NK020(wa)002:1297: sna chen dkar ljang thod khrag 'thung //
NK020(wa)002:1298: chu lha sngon mo sbrul zhags can //
NK020(wa)002:1299: rdo rje nag mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK020(wa)002:1300: rdo rje ser mo ra mgo zhags //
NK020(wa)002:1301: rdo rje dmar mo lcags sgrog sdom //
NK020(wa)002:1302: rdo rje ljang nag dril 'khrol dgyes //
NK020(wa)002:1303: 'bar ba'i gdan la mchod bzhes ru lu 'bar ma rnams kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK020(wa)002:1304: sku mdog gdul bya'i tshul 'dra zhing //
NK020(wa)002:1305: g.yas pa rdo rje 'bar ba ste //
NK020(wa)002:1307: 'bar ba'i mchod ru lu mkha' 'gro rnams kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK020(wa)002:1308: rdo rje gshog pas zil gnon cing //
NK020(wa)002:1311: 'bar ba'i mchod bzhes ru lu ma bdun sring bzhi'i phyag rgya ni //
NK020(wa)002:1312: 'jo sgeg mdzes dmar zol gyis lta /
NK020(wa)002:1314: g.yon pa dung khrag 'thung byed pa'o //
NK020(wa)002:1315: 'bar ba'i mchod bzhes ru lu rdo rje ging chen bco brgyad ni //
NK020(wa)002:1316: sngo skya 'jigs pa'i tshul ston cing //
NK020(wa)002:1317: g.yas pa gri dang mtshon cha thogs //
NK020(wa)002:1318: g.yon pas 'dzin cing gsod par byed //
NK020(wa)002:1319: 'bar ba'i mchod bzhes ru pho nya sum brgya drug cu'i tshul //
NK020(wa)002:1320: dkar dang sngo dang dmar dang nag /
NK020(wa)002:1321: gser dang byu ru'i mdog 'dra ba //
NK020(wa)002:1322: drug cu drug gis rdzogs pa ni //
NK020(wa)002:1323: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dang /
NK020(wa)002:1324: tho ba gshog pa gtun tshogs 'dzin //
NK020(wa)002:1325: ma lus khyab pa'i tshul gyis gnas //
NK020(wa)002:1326: 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK020(wa)002:1327: mchod bzhes dam skongs dngos grub stsol //
NK020(wa)002:1328: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h+aum ma h+aa mu dra h'u /
NK020(wa)002:1330: gzung 'dzin rnam rtog dngos po cir snang yang //
NK020(wa)002:1331: phyag rgya'i mchod pa phul ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK020(wa)002:1332: phyag rgya rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub nas kyang //
NK020(wa)002:1333: thams cad phyag rgya chen por lhun grub shog /
NK020(wa)002:1337: 'khor ba rgya mtsho'i yo byad rnams //
NK020(wa)002:1339: 'gro don ma lus lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK020(wa)002:1341: bzlas pa'i dus so so'i sngags bsgyur ba tsam las
NK020(wa)002:1342: gzhan go bgo lus srung gi bar sgrub thabs kyi
NK020(wa)002:1343: dkyus ltar bya ba yin no //
NK020(wa)002:1344: de bzhin du dkyil chog kyang sgrub dbang kho na'i
NK020(wa)002:1345: tshe sa chog mi dgos na'ang rtsa dkyil logs sgrub
NK020(wa)002:1346: lta bu'i tshe spyir dri med 'od phreng ba ltar
NK020(wa)002:1347: las / khyad par sa sbyang ba zung dang //
NK020(wa)002:1348: lha bum lta gon gyi bskyed bya rten dang brten
NK020(wa)002:1349: pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi khyad par bsgyur ba tsam las
NK020(wa)002:1350: gzhan med do // mdo yongs rdzogs kyi dbang du
NK020(wa)002:1351: byas pa'i yan lag gi dkyil 'khor brgyad pa a
